Date: 16/10/2025
Author: Uttam Cadambi Padmanaban

This is used to demonstrate the working of blockMesh. 

There are two cases:
1. Flat plate boundary layer
2. Cylinder.

Use the runMesh.sh (by typing ./runMesh in the terminal) and pick the case of your choice.

Please ensure that the OpenFOAM environment is sourced before running the bash script. 
